Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Good afternoon! This is Alex from Nexiv Solutions. Am I speaking with Sarah?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, this is Sarah. How can I help you?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Hi Sarah! Thanks for taking the time to speak with me today. I understand you’re the IT manager over at Global Ventures, correct?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, that's right.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Fantastic. At Nexiv Solutions, we specialize in streamlining IT operations and enhancing cybersecurity. I wanted to touch base with you to see if there are any areas you're looking to improve or any challenges you're currently facing?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Well, we're actually having a hard time with our data backup process. It's time-consuming and often unreliable.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I see. That’s a common concern we hear. An efficient, reliable backup process is crucial. Are you currently using any specific solutions for backups?

Speaker: Customer
Text: We're using an in-house system, but it's outdated. We’ve experienced a few failures recently, and it's causing a lot of stress on the team.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That sounds frustrating. Reliable data backup is essential for peace of mind. If I may ask, how much time does your team spend dealing with these backup issues on a weekly basis?

Speaker: Customer
Text: I'd say at least 10 to 15 hours a week. It’s significant time that could be better spent on other projects.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Absolutely. That's a substantial amount of lost productivity. At Nexiv Solutions, we offer a cloud-based backup system that automates the entire process and provides real-time monitoring and alerts. It would drastically reduce the time your team spends managing backups and increase overall reliability.

Speaker: Customer
Text: That sounds great but switching systems can be a hassle. I’m worried about the transition period and potential downtime.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That’s a valid concern. We have a dedicated implementation team that works closely with your IT department to ensure a seamless transition with minimal downtime. We also offer 24/7 support to handle any issues that might arise.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Okay, that does sound reassuring. I'm just cautious because we've had bad experiences with transitions in the past.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I completely understand, Sarah. To ease your concerns, we can start with a pilot program. This will allow you to test our solution on a smaller scale before fully committing. You’ll be able to see firsthand how it works and the benefits it brings.

Speaker: Customer
Text: A pilot program sounds like a good idea. How long would this pilot last?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Typically, our pilot programs run for 30 days. During this period, we'll provide full support and training to ensure your team feels comfortable and confident using the system.

Speaker: Customer
Text: That seems reasonable. What would be the next steps if we decide to proceed?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: If you’re ready, I can send over a proposal outlining the details of the pilot program, including timelines and support structure. Once you review and approve it, we can get started as early as next week. Does that work for you?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, let’s do that. Please send over the proposal, and I'll review it with our team.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Great, I’ll have that sent to your email by the end of the day. Thanks for your time, Sarah. Looking forward to working with you.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Thank you, Alex. I appreciate your help.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: My pleasure. Have a great day, Sarah.

Speaker: Customer
Text: You too, goodbye.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Goodbye.
